body:
Howdy folks! 
Welcome to Ambi's unofficial tourney! This one is going to be a bit different, instead of have teams registering, the event coordinators will be creating teams from the players registered. So you will be playing with new players (similar to a ranked match). 

Tournament Gamemode: CTW (Capture the wool)

Fielding and method: The tournament will be single-elimination. Maximum roster sizes are 8, the amount on the field are a minimum of 4 and a maximum of 6. 
We will try to give each team a defender, etc...

Map Pool:
You will find out just before your match. This is to add quick thinking and stratting from the leader.


IMPORTANT Dates:
1st stage - 16th July
Semi Finals - 23rd July
Finals and 3rd place - 30th July

Event staff;
Moooody (Official)
Kyoal (Official) 
Nathy_ (Referee)
LFT (Referee)
 
Registration:
CLOSED

LEADERS APPLICATIONS CLOSED

CHALLONGE:
http://challonge.com/ambitournament

Good luck and have fun folks!
